10","replies":52,"created_ts":1657162236,"created":"10:50:36","title":"初次用 bbr，很惊喜","author":"zephyr1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zephyr1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7c0a80a17b7d95d4d963492c9cbd42ff?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":864576,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","description":"<p>这个不走寻常路的地址栏以及左边那个放荡不羁的向上箭头真的是专治强迫症，我已经麻了，困扰多年的强迫症奇迹般好转</p>\n<p><img alt=\"lol\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/07/BfrEKtz7SXpVQN9.jpg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/864576","replies":51,"created_ts":1657142462,"created":"05:21:02","title":"感谢微软治好了我多年的强迫症 😣","author":"MajestySolor","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MajestySolor","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e89c/8c25/17318_mini.png?m=1653685292"},{"id":864652,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"信息安全本科，编程水平一般。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/864652","replies":44,"created_ts":1657170410,"created":"13:06:50","title":"计算机转去做生物信息学怎么样，属不属于降维打击？","author":"DadLearnpython","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DadLearnpython","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9a77/52de/580946_mini.png?m=1656856160"},{"id":864593,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598","description":"<p>MacOS Monterey<br/>\n版本:12.4<br/>\nMacBookPro 14 2021<br/>\n芯片 M1Pro<br/>\n内存 32G  </p>\n<p>最近一段时间使用的时候,经常发现内存占用比较高,打开任务管理器发现是通知中心占用比较大\n目前常用的就是强制结束进程</p>\n<p><img alt=\"RUNOOB 图标\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i3yxxyo_d.webp?maxwidth=1520&amp;fidelity=grand\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/864593","replies":42,"created_ts":1657158217,"created":"09:43:37","title":"想问问你们的 mac 内存使用率","author":"chrosing","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chrosing","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9ca8be48214f51396acd0e1aeafe74f2?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":864607,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","description":"<p>总的来说目前是不推荐使用，特别是手机暂不支持广电 5G 。</p>\n<p>号码购买 - WX 小程序，可以选择任意地区，快递全国送（好评\n订单查询 - 下单不限制登陆，下单后查询不到订单，客服也查不到（差评\n卡号激活 - 大坑，需要输入手机号码(订单都查不到，要是你不记得选的 11 位数字那就。。身份证识别正面是国徽，背面是人像。。拍的照片不能离太近太近就识别失败，要把身份证拍的小小的才成功。。</p>\n<p>我的两个手机 - 华为 Meta20Pro 、iPhone13Pro\n华为 Meta20Pro - 目前看是不在广电支持的列表内，插上卡刚开始有信号一会就无服务了（大概原因手机设置里面没有启用 VOLTE 的开关导致）\niPhone13Pro - 插卡无服务， 语音与数据选择 LET 并启用 VoLTE （所以才判断 Meta20 无服务是因为开不了 VoLTE 导致的）</p>\n<p>使用中发现型号极其的差，完全不能满足正常使用。\n办公室有信号勉强能用，测速的速度很慢，聊聊微信没问题，中午出去吃饭就无服务了。。\n在成都市区大多数地方也是无服务，简直就是个辣🐔</p>\n<p>网速情况 - 下载 20-60Mbps 上传 0-10Mbps</p>\n<p>Meta20 上有个移动卡，大家都是 4G 网络，从周一到现在用下来，移动在我到过的所有地方都有信号可以刷抖音</p>\n<p>今天早上想起来可以设置接入点，再观察观察设置接入点后，看看能不能做到和移动 4G 一样\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h3y4qh7ue7j20vo0u0dhp.jpg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/864607","replies":38,"created_ts":1657161706,"created":"10:41:46","title":"广电卡体验交流（买了的大冤种进","author":"MsHan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MsHan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3c47/1a7f/255357_mini.png?m=1657160334"}]